that he's sort of lost,
which is definitely true.</i>

00:25.334 --> 00:27.318
<i>In fact, a lot of the New
Directions have no idea
what they're doing,</i>

00:27.369 --> 00:28.836
<i>and graduation is right around
the corner.</i>

00:28.921 --> 00:30.755
<i>They should change their name
to the No Directions.</i>

00:30.822 --> 00:31.923
