I was just conferring
with my co-judge,

11:07.976 --> 11:11.895
and our three finalists
for the suit are

11:11.963 --> 11:13.147
Santana Lopez...

11:13.231 --> 11:14.481
(applause)

11:14.566 --> 11:15.298
Mercedes Jones...

11:15.350 --> 11:17.467
(cheering)
and...

11:17.519 --> 11:18.569
Finn Hudson.

11:20.105 --> 11:21.488
What?

11:21.573 --> 11:22.940
Give it up.

11:22.991 --> 11:24.908
Come on.
Yeah.

11:25.948 --> 11:25.948
+

11:28.254 --> 11:30.038
Congrats, guys.
You three are the finalists

11:30.089 --> 11:31.256
of the Saturday Night Fever
Dance Competition.

11:31.340 --> 11:32.507
Whoo!

11:32.575 --> 11:33.592
High stakes here.

11:33.676 --> 11:35.043
Which one of you
will walk away

11:35.094 --> 11:36.211
with Sue's coveted
white suit?

11:36.262 --> 11:37.178
Sounds kind of
cool to me.

11:37.246 --> 11:38.296
Oh, great.
It's yours.

11:38.381 --> 11:39.414
Can we go now?

11:39.465 --> 11:40.415
Okay, look.

11:40.466 --> 11:42.100
This isn't really about a suit.

11:42.184 --> 11:43.768
It's about living
out your dreams.

11:43.853 --> 11:45.687
Of all the seniors
in New Directions,

11:45.754 --> 11:47.439
you three have
yet to decide

11:47.523 --> 11:49.190
what it is you want to do
with your lives.

11:49.258 --> 11:50.609
So your assignment
for the week:

11:50.693 --> 11:52.760
<i>perform a song
from Saturday Night Fever,</i>

11:52.812 --> 11:55.146
and then share your hopes
for the future.

11:55.231 --> 11:56.731
No, wait.
The dance thing is fixed?

11:56.782 --> 11:58.650
So what is this,
some teacher's

11:58.734 --> 12:00.151
manipulative game
to get us tell you

12:00.236 --> 12:02.037
what we want to be
when we grow up?

12:02.104 --> 12:03.805
Hey, if you want to look
at it that way, fine.

12:03.873 --> 12:05.907
But this is
your game,
your life.

12:05.958 --> 12:08.877
And guess what,
time's running out.

12:08.944 --> 12:10.545
(bell ringing)

12:10.613 --> 12:12.247
<i>MERCEDES:
Where does Mr. Shue get off</i>

12:12.298 --> 12:14.249
<i>telling me how to have a dream?</i>

12:14.300 --> 12:16.618
<i>Just because I don't want
to rush off to New York</i>

12:16.669 --> 12:19.054
<i>like Berry and star
in a revival of Sister Act</i>

12:19.121 --> 12:21.890
<i>doesn't mean I don't know
what I want to do with my life.</i>

12:21.957 --> 12:23.925
